Global Cableway Transport Market Insights
Cableway Transport Market size was valued at USD 8.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 12.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Cableway Transport Market Overview
The global cableway transport market is witnessing substantial growth, with an estimated market size valued at USD 13.5 billion in 2024. The demand for cableway transport systems, such as cable cars, gondolas, and aerial trams, has been expanding rapidly, particularly in the tourism, urban mobility, and mountain transportation sectors. The adoption of eco-friendly transport solutions, increasing investment in tourism infrastructure, and the need for efficient urban transport systems are driving market growth. By 2032, the market is projected to reach USD 23.2 billion, growing at a CAGR of 7.3% during the forecast period.

